We are currently looking for an advisor / data analyst to join our team of experts. He will be in charge of developing, integrating and validating data flows in a cloud environment on behalf of BI solution customers.

Main responsibilities
Study statistical data to produce business recommendations;
Build and distribute BI and web analytics reports;
Master analysis tools to enable internal decision-makers to monitor the performance of sites or products;
Find the relevant data sources;
Process the various data concerning customers, products or the performance of the company in order to identify useful indicators for decision-makers.
Extraction and translation of business data into statistical data,
Synthesize and popularize information to make it accessible to company managers,
Facilitate business decision-making by providing an advisory role.

